# Keep the build context (and image) small. frontend/ IS needed (served at /app);
# only its tests are dropped.
**/venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/htmlcov
**/.coverage
**/*.db
.git
.github
backend/tests
frontend/tests
docs
*.md
# NOTE: do not exclude deploy/ — the backup image build (deploy/backup/Dockerfile)
# COPYs deploy/backup/backup.sh from this shared context. The app image simply
# doesn't COPY deploy/, so keeping it in-context costs nothing.
